- May I ask how your holiday is going?
- Very well, thank you.

02:50.420 --> 02:52.212
You've been coming here long?

02:53.590 --> 02:56.341
I've been coming here for about twenty years.

02:57.051 --> 03:00.846
I used to come with my wife
and now I keep coming on my own.

03:00.972 --> 03:03.849
