will be simply ecstatic ...

04:40.905 --> 04:43.949
... To hear you conduct your famous
"Simple Songs".

04:46.327 --> 04:50.455
I wil not conduct
my "Simple Songs".

04:51.165 --> 04:53.083
Why not?

04:53.459 --> 04:55.961
Personal reasons.

04:57.213 --> 05:00.340
The great soprano Sumi Jo
has agreed to sing.

05:00.466 --> 05:02.050
Sumi Jo won't do.

05:02.468 --> 05:05.595
Tell me which soprano will do
and you should have her.

05:08.057 --> 05:09.933
No one will do.

05:42.258 --> 05:43.884
Very well.

05:44.010 --> 05:46.970
I shall relay our conversation
to the Queen.

05:51.017 --> 05:53.352
Good day, Maestro.

06:09.160 --> 06:11.036
Do you see that?

06:11.913 --> 06:14.039
Is that him?

06:14.165 --> 06:15.749
Why yes...

06:16.000 --> 06:18.502
It is! God!

06:20.546 --> 06:22.547
Angela!

07:49.594 --> 07:52.220
Melanie! Melanie!

09:02.041 --> 09:05.168
I was thinking today how You
and I have the same problem.

09:05.336 --> 09:08.964
- Is that so? - We've been
misunderstood our whole lives ...

09:09.090 --> 09:15.345
... because we are allowed ourselves
to give in just once to a little levity.

09:15.471 --> 09:18.723
Levity is an
irresistible temptation.

09:21.686 --> 09:26.231
I worked with all the great
European and American directors...

09:27.483 --> 09:31.111
... But I'll be remembered
forever for "Mister Q".

09:31.696 --> 09:34.322
For a fucking robot.

09:34.490 --> 09:39.119
I had to wear suit of armour
that weighted two hundred pounds.

09:39.245 --> 09:40.745
You couldn't even see my face.

09:40.871 --> 09:44.124
But every five minutes somebody
has to come up and remind me ...

09:44.250 --> 09:46.209
... I did "Mister Q".

09:46.502 --> 09:51.089
The same way they remind You
that You did the "Simple Songs".

09:52.508 --> 09:54.342
And they forget ...

09:54.635 --> 09:57.971
That you also composed
"The Black Prism" ...

09:58.764 --> 10:01.516
