10:02.602 --> 10:05.103
Because levity also ...

10:05.271 --> 10:07.230
A perversion.

10:10.026 --> 10:12.235
What are you doing in Europe?

10:13.237 --> 10:17.032
I'm doing a new film in Germany.
Starting in a month.

10:17.783 --> 10:22.162
- I am developing the role.
- Is it a light-hearted role?

10:22.288 --> 10:24.289
That depends on your point of view.

10:24.790 --> 10:26.791
And is all going well?

10:30.296 --> 10:31.796
We'll see.

10:33.549 --> 10:36.384
Well, it's late for me.

10:36.510 --> 10:38.136
Not for me.

10:38.262 --> 10:39.679
Good night.

